<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201111/8dbc4494be0143ed8e2811a18a45c8ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>网友纷纷签到留念</strong></p>
